formance across the full spectral\nformat, which, combined with intrinsic thermal stability requirements for EPRV\nscience, has driven the selection of silicon optics and Invar optomechanics.\nThe system performance is further optimized using precision (sub-mK) thermal\ncontrol. This set of design features will allow iLocater to achieve sub-m/s\nradial velocity precision in the near-infrared, and to serve as the first\noptimized diffraction-limited spectrograph for EPRV science.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2022 18:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-02"}
