ons smaller than some other\ncritical size, the island does not emerge. Finally, we show that the island\nprescription does not help to solve the information paradox for certain finite\nsize regions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2022 18:01:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 Sep 2022 16:31:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 27 Mar 2023 17:46:27 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 23 May 2023 11:24:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-24"}
