ing\nthis model with LSST would be challenging. However, taking into account a speed\nof sound $c_s<1$ of the dark energy fluid can make this model observable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Sep 2022 13:24:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-15"}
